{"ts":"2026-07-19T03:42:53.329Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"append","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/body","value":"GH-611. pm delete removes .toon but appends a delete op to history/<id>.jsonl (file kept). Delete-on-A vs edit-on-B merge: git delete/modify resolution keeps B's .toon → deleted item silently resurrects; history left with conflict markers; validate ok:true. Fix direction: validate flags live .toon whose history ends in delete op (resurrection candidate) + conflict-marker scan in history files; document delete-vs-edit merge policy."},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-19T03:42:53.329Z"}],"before_hash":"608fab66fb6c93962471bd28669d12650c76eda3884629d8c5690ecfda323d2b","after_hash":"c4344e466a5efec562ea127b8924ee958af46459f3be38f190aaddbf4bec7e3a"}
